{"tid":1696572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好放棄，禮拜五朝早仲有抗爭活動","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T03:38:42.000Z","uid":219269,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"eb109426bda55aa6ade16a3838c4ab221cefc3bb","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"我係上次和你返工嘅搞手之一<br />\n好多謝大家賞面參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白大家想罷工嘅心情<br />\n可能有人一開波就屌我仲返工<br />\n但唔緊要，呢個行動嘅目的係希望將抗爭蔓延去平日早上<br />\n有心嘅手足我鼓勵你地搞更多更大更進取嘅行動<br />\n正如天崎所講，覺得有用就要去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係行動嘅詳情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvqxmEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmvqxmEy.jpg&h=8c85d5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvYyQxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvYyQxU.jpg&h=e2245eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gotoworktogether\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgotoworktogether&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2fe54130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gotoworktogether</a>"},{"pid":"ff311789b640860d9e70feb3d6d14aa2a8aab084","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"1108 和你返工2.0 <br />\n所有路線0745集合 0800準時起步<br />\n<br />\n九龍西集合點<br />\n1. 旺角C4 朗豪坊<br />\n往尖沙咀方向：經彌敦道，到達sogo外解散<br />\n2. 尖沙咀 半島集合 <br />\n往旺角方向，滙豐解散<br />\n3. 楓樹街遊樂場<br />\n往荔枝角，沿長沙灣道，長沙灣廣場解散<br />\n<br />\n九龍東集合點<br />\n1. 九龍灣A<br />\n2. 觀塘A<br />\n雙向行走：經觀塘道<br />\n<br />\n港島區<br />\n<br />\n1. 上環E4<br />\n<br />\n2. 銅鑼灣E（東西雙線）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;雙向行走：經軒尼詩道、金鐘道、德輔道中（以上各為解散地點）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;往太古坊：經英皇道，太古坊解散<br />\n<br />\n3. 太古城（admin @dontrumpjrii 負責聯絡）<br />\n經英皇道，皇仁書院解散<br />\n<br />\n新界東<br />\n1. 大圍A<br />\n2. 沙田新城市近黨鐵站<br />\n雙向行走：經村南道、文禮路、希爾頓、新城市<br />\n（各為解散點）<br />\n<br />\n新界西<br />\n1. 葵芳D <br />\n經興芳路、葵富路、葵涌道，葵興站解散"},{"pid":"bbee26dbc3583229c663fc5e441ba5259f41e7f0","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e44d67ced383d9682edfb982ba3aa9063cc776fe","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd2f2c4792b881106e578f138bd477f6bec1764f","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20df8930bd02e346e00b33651f67eb7e1b8e59e8","tid":1696572,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb4047b627186a1ba1bdff199c6506a8c708606","tid":1696572,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7425365c89980b937d22367457f3bff7847cac8","tid":1696572,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"今次終於有得行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21535a9fce8a344208dfb067c7d65d8b1640a5b0","tid":1696572,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"推，今次要多人過上次"},{"pid":"6085faf6d6c3588d209a5d2974e9d309629c17b4","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27b155d19c7318e3c8f813e57fd25cc210b14b1c","tid":1696572,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"早起早起早起!"},{"pid":"79e1a6f8565f40dc8ee1699522a000061ab4e33e","tid":1696572,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df8db2